<p align="center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200815/701525a4062c4e30ada802bee544be8f.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">直播带货，志愿者们各显所能推销番鸭。</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200815/893811fc724c4784a161dcce882578fb.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
